# RDF Content Negotiation

* assigned: bonfacem
* status: in-progress

## Description

We should be able to receive different formats from virtuoso:

```
curl -H "Accept: application/ld+json" https://rdf.genenetwork.org/v1/id/Arabidopsis_thaliana
```

Moreover, we should get rid off (Note the "n6"):

=> http://rdf.genenetwork.org/v1/term/shortName n6:shortName

## Resolution

* https://git.genenetwork.org/gn-guile/commit/?id=a770f96a9e36f1272418870d1cddc2bd2f5c2b17

See all global namespaces:

```
  SELECT  NS_PREFIX, 
          NS_URL 
    FROM  DB.DBA.SYS_XML_PERSISTENT_NS_DECL
ORDER BY  LOWER(NS_PREFIX) ;
```

